# U-Boot environment location — SD card (mmcblk0)
#
# Format: device  offset  size  sector-size  [count]
# Redundant environment: two copies at consecutive offsets for robustness.
#
# TODO: Verify these offsets against the moto-timo/meta-raspberrypi fork's
#       U-Boot defconfig (CONFIG_ENV_OFFSET / CONFIG_ENV_OFFSET_REDUND).
#       If the fork uses CONFIG_ENV_IS_IN_FAT, replace these raw-offset entries
#       with the FAT-file form:  /dev/mmcblk0p1  -  -  -  uboot.env
#
# Primary environment copy at 2 MB, redundant at 2 MB + 16 KB
/dev/mmcblk0 0x200000 0x4000 0x1000
/dev/mmcblk0 0x204000 0x4000 0x1000
